Santa Fe Hill Climb
description: Santa Fe Hill Climb, Starts at Fort Marcy Rec Complex, ends at the Santa Fe Ski Basin.
course: The course is 14.7 miles with 3300 Feet of elevation gain.
registration: All categories will race 14.7 miles. \"A\" race, men 1,2,3 \"B\" Race Men 3,4 \"C\" Men 4,5 D Men Masters 50+, \"E\" Women 1,2,3 and Women 4.  All women will start together, cat 4 will be scored separately. Juniors will start with their category, merchandise prizes. Send completed release form to Stephen Newhall 601 West San Mateo, unit 92, Santa Fe Nm 87505 $10 Discount for pre registration, must be recieved by July 23. $10 one day license available.
notes: No personal follow cars! This is a narrow winding road, there will be no wheel support, carry a spare tube.
directions: Take Paseo De Peralta off of NM 84/285 (St. Francis Dr). Turn north on Washington Ave (by the big pink church) turn left into Fort Marcy Rec Complex at Artist Road.
